                        Harriman
                    ) to the Secretary of
                            State</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945v05</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d482</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">482</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-02-21T05:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-02-21T05:00:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc>            <textClass>
